<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <title>YouTube to Mp3 Converter </title>
</head>

<body>
   

    <!-- Top Container-->
    <div class="top-container">
        <div id="dark-mode-switch">
            <div id="dark-mode-switch-btn" onclick="dark_mode()">
            <p>Mode: <span id="mode-text">Light</span> </p>
              <div id="dark-mode-switch-toggle"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

        <form action="/convert-mp3" method="POST" id="form">
            <h1 id="header_1"><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i>Youtube To Mp3 Converter</h1>
            <h4 style="font-size: 11pt; display: flex; justify-content: center;">Please insert a valid YouTube video URL</h4>
            <div id="input-placeholder">
                <input type="text" name="videoID" placeholder="e.g. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=videoID"><button id="convert-button">Convert</button>
            </div>
        </form>

    </div>
    

    <!-- Container to show song details and error message-->
    <div class="bottom-container">
        <% if(typeof success != "undefined" && success) { %>
            <div class="success">
                <p><%= song_title %></p>
                <a href="<%= song_link %>"><button id="download-btn">DOWNLOAD</button></a>
            </div>
            <% } else if(typeof success != "undefined" && !success) { %>
                <div class="errors">
                    <p><%= message %></p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            
    </div>

    <!--Site info container-->

    <!-- FAQ1 -->
    <div id="faq-section">
        <div id="faq-main-header">FAQ</div>
        <div class="faq-container" onclick="toggleAnswer('faq1')">
        <div class="faq-header"  id="faq1">
            <div class="faq-question">What is YouTube To Mp3 Converter?</div>
            <div class="faq-expand-symbol" id="expand-symbol-faq1">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq1-answer">
            <p>YouTube.com is the largest video sharing platform on the <br>
                internet. Every day millions of new videos are added. You <br>
                can find all kinds of videos but YouTube does not offer a <br>
                FREE downloading service for these videos <br> <br>
                YouTube To Mp3 Converter allows you to downlaod your favourite YouTube <br>
                videos as MP3 (audio) files in the most efficient way. <br>
                You are able to use YouTube To Mp3 Converter on any device <br>
                it is optimized to work on desktop, tablet and mobile devices. <br>
                There is also no additional software or app needed. <br>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- FAQ2 -->
        <div class="faq-container" onclick="toggleAnswer('faq2')">
        <div class="faq-header" id="faq2">
            <div class="faq-question">How to downlaod YouTube videos?</div>
            <div class="faq-expand-symbol" id="expand-symbol-faq2">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq2-answer">
            <p><b>1.</b> Open YouTube.com and search for the video you <br>
                would like to download. <br><br>
               <b>2.</b> When you find the video, click on it and wait until it <br>
               starts  playing. Then, just copy the video URL from your <br>
               browser address bar.<br><br>
               <b>3.</b> Open <u>YouTube To MP3 Converter</u> and paste the video URL in our <br>
               converter. Then, simply click on the "Convert" button. The <br>
               conversion will be initiated, and may take a few minutes to<br>
               convert your chosen video into an MP3 format. <br>
               We will try to convert the video in the best available <br>
               quality. But be aware that it is only possible to download <br>
               videos that are up to 10 minutes long, to guarantee that <br>
               the conversion will be done within a few minutes. <br><br>
               <b>4.</b> As soon as the convertion of the video is completed <br>
               you will see a "Downlaod" button. Just click on it, and the <br>
               download shall start. Enjoy! <br> 
               
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- FAQ3 -->
        <div class="faq-container" onclick="toggleAnswer('faq3')">
        <div class="faq-header" id="faq3"> 
            <div class="faq-question">Which video platforms are supported?</div>
            <div class="faq-expand-symbol" id="expand-symbol-faq3">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq3-answer">
            <p>Our Wev-App supports YouTube. These kinds of YouTube video <br>
                URLs are accepted by our converter: <br>
                <b>-</b> youtube.com/watch?v=videoId <br>
                <b>-</b> youtu.be/videoId<br>
                <b>-</b> youtube.com/shorts/videoId <br>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- FAQ4 -->
    <div class="faq-container" onclick="toggleAnswer('faq4')">
        <div class="faq-header" id="faq4"> 
            <div class="faq-question">Is there a video length limit?</div>
            <div class="faq-expand-symbol" id="expand-symbol-faq4">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq4-answer">
            <p>Yes. Is is only posible to download YouTube videos <br>
