            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ5 -->
    <div class="faq-container" onclick="toggleAnswer('faq5')">
        <div class="faq-header" id="faq5"> 
            <div class="faq-question">Where is the mp3 file saved?</div>
            <div class="faq-expand-symbol" id="expand-symbol-faq5">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq5-answer">
            <p>You may check your browser settings. There you will <br>
