    <div class="faq-container" onclick="toggleAnswer('faq7')">
        <div class="faq-header" id="faq7"> 
            <div class="faq-question">What if the conversion doesn't start?</div>
            <div class="faq-expand-symbol" id="expand-symbol-faq7">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq7-answer">
            <p>Please delete your browser cache and reload the <br>
                site. Should the conversion still not start please send <br>
                us a message using our <u>contact form</u>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ8 -->
    <div class="faq-container" onclick="toggleAnswer('faq8')">
        <div class="faq-header" id="faq8"> 
            <div class="faq-question">Why conversion doesn't stop proccessing?</div>
            <div class="faq-expand-symbol" id="expand-symbol-faq8">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq8-answer">
            <p>
                In case a message saying "processing" appears, and it doen't stop <br>
                 refresh the page and try converting your video again. <br>
                 This should fix the issue <br>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ9 -->
    <div class="faq-container" onclick="toggleAnswer('faq9')">
        <div class="faq-header" id="faq9"> 
            <div class="faq-question">Is there a downlaod limit?</div>
            <div class="faq-expand-symbol" id="expand-symbol-faq9">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq9-answer">
            <p>
                Yes. Our app has a limit of 200 downlaods per day <br>
                and that's only to ensure security. <br>
                If the website reaches more traffic, we will allow more <br>
                downloads per day. So share YouTube To Mp3 Converter with friends!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ10 -->
    <div class="faq-container" onclick="toggleAnswer('faq10')">
        <div class="faq-header" id="faq10"> 
            <div class="faq-question">What if an error occurs?</div>
            <div class="faq-expand-symbol" id="expand-symbol-faq10">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer" id="faq10-answer">
            <p>
                Please be sure that you do not try to downlaod a <br>
                YouTube video that is a: <br>
                <b>-</b> livestream <br>
                <b>-</b> longer than 10 minutes <br>
                <b>-</b> private <br><br>
                If your video does not match any of the above listed <br>
                reasons and you are stil getting an error please <br>
                report it using out <u>contact form</u>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    


    </div><!-- FAQ Container End-->

    

    <hr class="line-section">

    
